Abstract Factory Pattern is a type of design pattern where an instance of factory from one central builder.
Factory Pattern is specific to its design, where as Abstract Factory Pattern is factory of factory
where it gives factory to create specific products.
It is generally designed and use in order to prevent manual generation from scratch.

A real life example:
    Choosing nepali factory to purchase a flour which is really efficient in time and quality rather than producing own flour.

Everything is done behind the scene and it is ready to be used whenever needed.

In this code example:
    AbstractFurnitureFactory is responsible to create FurnitureFactory based on FurnitureExporter.
    It has three exporters: Nepali, Indian and Chinese

    Once desired factory is build, we can create furniture like chair and sofa.